      "text": "Matrix is an open standard for interoperable, decentralised, real-time communication over IP. It can be used anywhere you need a standard HTTP API for publishing and subscribing to data whilst tracking the conversation history - [http://matrix.org/docs/guides/faq.html#general matrix.org]"
