        "text": "Matrix provides the following [http://matrix.org/docs/spec/#client-server-api-v1 api's]\n* Open Standard HTTP APIs for [[JSON]] messages.\n* Client<->Server API\n* Server<->Server API"
      },
      "date": 1466945832372
